{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objcMembers"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LogFormatter"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LogFormatter"},{"type":"text","text":" uses a modular “builder” pattern, allowing you to construct log output by assembling different parts (e.g., tags, message, metadata) in any order. Each part can be customized with prefixes, suffixes, and its own internal formatting."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Default Format","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default formatter produces logs in the following structure:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["Date [InternalTags] [LogType.symbolicValue] [ExternalTags] Message {Metadata}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An example log output using the default format:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["2023-10-27 10:30:00 +0000 [function: login, line: 123] [D] User logged in {\"source\": \"LoginVC\"}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Customization"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can create a custom formatter to rearrange parts, change separators, or filter tags. For example, to produce the above log output using a custom formatter having the following structure:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["[LogType.symbolicValue] [InternalTags] [ExternalTags] Message"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a new one using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LogFormatter.Builder"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let myFormatter = LogFormatter.Builder()","    .addTagsPart(prefix: \"[\", suffix: \"] \", filter: { $0.identifier.uppercased() == \"DEBUG\" }) \/\/ Matches the symbolic tag","    .addTagsPart(prefix: \"[\", format: { \"\\($0.identifier): \\($0.value)\" }, suffix: \"] \", filter: { $0.tagType == .internal })","    .addTagsPart(prefix: \"[\", separator: \", \", suffix: \"] \")","    .addMessagePart(prefix: \"The \", suffix: \".\")","    .build()"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Now, the same log output will appear like the following:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["[D] [function: login, line: 123] The User logged in."],"type":"codeListing"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Even though the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LogMessage"},{"type":"text","text":" have the date & metadata as well but just because custom formatter doesn’t include it. It will not appear in the final log output."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftLogSmith\/documentation\/SwiftLogSmith"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftLogSmith\/documentation\/SwiftLogSmith\/LogFormatter"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Classes","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftLogSmith\/documentation\/SwiftLogSmith\/LogFormatter\/Builder"],"anchor":"Classes"},{"title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftLogSmith\/documentation\/SwiftLogSmith\/LogFormatter\/format(message:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods"},{"title":"Type Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftLogSmith\/documentation\/SwiftLogSmith\/LogFormatter\/default"],"anchor":"Type-Properties"}],"metadata":{"title":"LogFormatter","symbolKind":"class","modules":[{"name":"SwiftLogSmith"}],"roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","